<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Recipe 1: Lasagna</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="container">
      <img src="/images/lasagna.jpg" alt="Lasagna" class="recipe-image" />
      <h1>Lasagna</h1>
      <p><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>12 lasagna noodles</li>
        <li>1 pound ground beef</li>
        <li>1 pound Italian sausage</li>
        <li>3 cups mozzarella cheese</li>
        <li>2 cups ricotta cheese</li>
        <li>1/2 cup grated Parmesan cheese</li>
        <li>1 jar marinara sauce</li>
        <li>Salt, Pepper, Basil, Oregano</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Instructions:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).</li>
        <li>Boil lasagna noodles, drain, and set aside.</li>
        <li>
          In a skillet, cook ground beef and sausage until browned. Drain excess
          fat.
        </li>
        <li>Stir in marinara sauce and seasonings. Simmer for 10 minutes.</li>
        <li>
          In a bowl, mix ricotta cheese, half of the mozzarella, Parmesan, and
          some herbs.
        </li>
        <li>
          Layer sauce, noodles, ricotta mixture, and mozzarella in a baking
          dish. Repeat layers.
        </li>
        <li>Bake for 45 minutes. Let it rest for 10 minutes before serving.</li>
      </ol>
      <a href="/">⬅️ Back to Home</a>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
